profile:
Provincial Building Services has completed some of the most challenging updates the country has ever seen. Company first opened its doors to clients in 1999. 

As the world has recently gotten smaller in the times of COVID the need for space solutions have never been greater.  Provincial Cabinetry seems too good to be true. At big box prices but with custom box quality. 100% solid wood cabinetry. Cabinet grade plywood boxes, solid wood doors and drawers all with custom style dovetail joinery.

LOCATION - VICTORIA, VANCOUVER, EDMONTON, SASKATOON, FORT MCMURRAY.
services:
Residential/Commercial Window Cleaning, Pressure Washing, Eavestrough Cleaning, 
Parkade Remediation and Cleaning, 
High Rise Remediation - Painting, Caulking and Window Replacement, Engineering Inspections - High Rope access of Glass Curtain Walls and Building Envelopes, 
High Rope Stand by Rescue and Supervision, Renovations - Bathrooms, Kitchens, Carpentry, Tiling, Roofing, Electrical, Plumbing, New Home Construction, Design and General Contracting
